        History
        =======
        
        0.1.0 (2017-03-08)
        ------------------
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        
        
        0.1.3
        -----
        
        * Added ability to pass a session into BaseMixin database methods.
        * Added ``dump_method`` decorator to allow custom methods to be called while
          creating the json representation.
        
